<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 12:40:19 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>琼斯表示，澳大利亚央行将数字代币的关注重点从“如果”转向“如何”</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-25/rba-shifting-focus-on-digital-tokens-from-if-to-how-jones-says</link><description>澳大利亚央行助理行长布拉德·琼斯表示，澳大利亚央行已将重点从批发数字代币是否会在金融体系中发挥作用转向如何实施，因为它希望在试点项目后释放效率收益。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/igoogbybOI3s/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 02:40:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-25/rba-shifting-focus-on-digital-tokens-from-if-to-how-jones-says</guid></item><item><title>加密货币交易者正在转变为大型跨资产追逐者</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-24/crypto-perps-platforms-are-increasingly-used-for-trading-tradfi-assets</link><description>Hyperliquid、Ostium 等网站发现传统资产永续资产占据了更大的交易量份额&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iViar1s5soj4/v9/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-24/crypto-perps-platforms-are-increasingly-used-for-trading-tradfi-assets</guid></item><item><title>加密巨头寻求审计，Tether 里程碑式的筹款活动被搁置</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-24/tether-s-landmark-fundraise-on-hold-as-crypto-giant-seeks-audit</link><description>Tether Holdings SA 筹集高达 200 亿美元的计划已暂停，这家稳定币巨头正在等待其首次全面财务审计的结果，此举可能会重启数字资产时代最受期待的筹款活动之一。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iscYrrRPyyGc/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 19:29:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-24/tether-s-landmark-fundraise-on-hold-as-crypto-giant-seeks-audit</guid></item><item><title>比特币的制度转变推动 Bernstein 买入 15 万美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-24/bitcoin-s-institutional-shift-drives-bernstein-s-150-000-call</link><description>Bernstein 表示，比特币很可能已经触底，到 2026 年底可能会升至 15 万美元，该公司认为，加密货币正在通过机构所有权和融资的稳步转变而被重塑。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iEyVmo9BBf4o/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 16:09:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-24/bitcoin-s-institutional-shift-drives-bernstein-s-150-000-call</guid></item><item><title>加密货币公司 Ledger 完成了价值 5000 万美元的二次股票出售</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-24/crypto-firm-ledger-completed-a-50-million-secondary-share-sale</link><description>总部位于巴黎的数字资产公司 Ledger 完成了价值 5000 万美元的二次股票出售，其首席执行官表示，该公司近期没有计划进行公开发行。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iTUUTYGCA5Ic/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 12:17:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-24/crypto-firm-ledger-completed-a-50-million-secondary-share-sale</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚养老基金罕见地考虑提供加密货币</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/australian-pension-fund-mulls-offering-crypto-in-rare-move</link><description>澳大利亚最大的养老基金之一 Hostplus 正在考虑向其成员提供加密货币作为投资选择，迄今为止，这一资产类别在很大程度上被其行业竞争对手所回避。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/icuz86zYya7A/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 23:15:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/australian-pension-fund-mulls-offering-crypto-in-rare-move</guid></item><item><title>华尔街支持的加密货币交易所利用韩元稳定币瞄准亚洲外汇市场</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/wall-street-backed-crypto-exchange-targets-asia-fx-market-using-won-stablecoin</link><description>由 Citadel 证券支持的加密货币交易所正在创建第一个基于区块链的韩元兑美元衍生品，这是亚洲最繁忙的货币对之一。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3bAKZRADnFI/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/wall-street-backed-crypto-exchange-targets-asia-fx-market-using-won-stablecoin</guid></item><item><title>Henry Kravis 支持的 ParaFi 新基金筹集 1.25 亿美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/henry-kravis-backed-parafi-raises-125-million-for-new-fund</link><description>ParaFi 是一家总部位于纽约的数字资产管理公司，其支持者包括 KKR &amp;amp; Co. 联合创始人亨利·克拉维斯 (Henry Kravis)，该公司告诉彭博社，该公司于 3 月份为一只新风险基金筹集了 1.25 亿美元。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ioQXnvew3Xc4/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 20:03:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/henry-kravis-backed-parafi-raises-125-million-for-new-fund</guid></item><item><title>特朗普给予伊朗谈判五天时间，比特币上涨</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/bitcoin-rises-after-trump-says-to-postpone-iran-strikes</link><description>在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示美国已开始与伊朗进行谈判后，比特币与股市一起上涨，而油价下跌，这增加了人们对达成协议以缓解冲突的希望。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iV70TN1fQsCU/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 11:21:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/bitcoin-rises-after-trump-says-to-postpone-iran-strikes</guid></item><item><title>瑞士私人银行王朝因加密战略冲突而分裂</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/swiss-private-bank-dynasty-splits-over-clashing-views-on-crypto</link><description>瑞士私人银行王朝正因公司未来愿景的代际分歧而陷入痛苦之中。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ioWHn.dGWqDw/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 05:15:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-23/swiss-private-bank-dynasty-splits-over-clashing-views-on-crypto</guid></item></channel></rss>